      <title>中国调查对冲基金产品收益达795%，但所有者失踪</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/china-probes-hedge-fund-with-795-product-gain-owner-missing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在对5.5万亿元人民币（7600亿美元）的行业进行更严格的审查后，中国正在对一家回报率出色的对冲基金公司进行调查，该公司停止偿还投资者的款项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-13/china-probes-hedge-fund-with-795-product-gain-owner-missing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 13 May 2024 08:38:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
